parameters: Citizen Kaga: Did you happen to see the bulletin board?

Mage Relm: Leave it to this great genius! So, where is this
man-eating bear?
Citizen Kaga: Well... I don't know!

Citizen Kaga: He's always popping up unexpectedly... First,
I want you to head to Marako Village.

Citizen Kaga: Please borrow the power of the hunter who is
there.

Mage Relm: That's fine, but why don't we defeat it when
there's a hunter around?

Citizen Kaga: The depletion of crystals in Valeria has taken
away dreams and hopes from the people who have lost hope.

Citizen Kaga: It's sad, but there are many people who treat
it as someone else's problem until they themselves are
attacked.

扉
EV086
炭鉱夫フィロ

parameters:
Coal miner Philo: Where did I drop it...? This is
troublesome.
Coal miner Philo: Did you check the bulletin board?
Clea: Leave it to us. Where should we go to search?

Coal miner Philo: I think it's near the work area... It's
not worth much, but it's my father's memento.
Clea: We will definitely find it!

Coal miner Philo: Y-Yeah... Thanks. Let me know when you're
ready.
Coal miner Philo: Are you ready?
Coal miner Philo: Let me know when you're ready.

Coal miner Philo: I'll guide you to the vicinity, so follow
me.
Thief Nora: I found a coin!

Miner Philo: Is that true...!? This is... without a doubt,
my late father's keepsake coin.

Miner Philo: Thank you so much! He may not have been a good
father, but he raised me, after all.
Clea: Please make sure you don't drop it again.

Miner Philo: Alright, I understand. I want you to receive
your reward.
Clea: It seems like the reward is generous.

Miner Philo: This is my gratitude for searching so
diligently. As an adventurer, I don't think you'll have any
trouble keeping it, right?
Clea: Yes, I will gratefully make use of it.

Coal miner Philo: I carry the coin you found with me at all
times.

the butler at Lord Oricto's mansion.'

attacked, we shouldn't lose!

Clea: I think it's worth going to check. I don't think we
would request a mission from the guild without any
negotiation material.

Clea: I hope to gather any information I can for the sake of
Armada-san.
Clea: However, let's not neglect our caution as we proceed.

parameters:
Valie Guard: Sigh, things have really taken a turn for the
worse... What should we do?
2.演出開始　【142】バリエ衛兵の体裁　1-2
3.イベント後のプレイヤーの位置
2.演出開始　【142】バリエ衛兵の体裁　1-2

Valier Guardsman: Please speak in a lower voice... That
request is something special... Show your face more often.

Valier Guardsman: Seems like quite the skilled individual.
You can trust them to handle special requests with ease.

Clea: I see... So I just need to bring back a fugitive named
Zagal, right?

Valier Guardsman: If we let the fugitive escape while
transporting them to Fotizona, it would be a huge blow to
the reputation of the Valier Guards...!

Valier Guardsman: The informants seem to know something, but
we can't afford to owe them any favors.

Clea: Understood. First, I will try contacting the
informant.
3.イベント後のプレイヤーの位置

Valie Guard: I'm counting on you for the sake of the Valie
Guard's reputation!
